  ##If you arrive in the UK before 11:59pm (UK time) on 16 April

  You will not need a Direct Airside Transit visa if:

  * you booked and paid for your journey to the UK before 12:01am (UK time) on 6 March 2026
  * you will not pass through border control

  You should bring evidence of your onward journey, such as a ticket to your destination.

  %You may want to apply for a [transit visa](/transit-visa) instead if you have a criminal record or you’ve previously been refused entry into the UK.
